// - Hover overlay (rgba): 'linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(91, 147, 215, 0.06) 0%, rgba(46, 90, 172, 0.08) 100%)'
// - Shared services container: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #E0EDFB 0%, #C7DDEF 100%)'
// - Icon backgrounds (small): 'linear-gradient(to bottom right, #5B93D7, #2E5AAC)'

// Info banners: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #F0F7FD 0%, #E0EDFB 100%)'
```

**Dashboard Gradient Hierarchy:**
1. Lightest (cards): #F0F7FD → #E0EDFB
2. Medium (containers): #E0EDFB → #C7DDEF  
3. Dark (icon accents): #5B93D7 → #2E5AAC
4. Darkest (headers): #5B93D7 → #2E5AAC → #1C3667

